WEBVTT

00:04.288 --> 00:07.114
Steven, hurry up!

00:07.691 --> 00:09.392
Are you okay?

00:09.493 --> 00:13.229
- I'm fine.
- Are you sure you're okay?

00:13.330 --> 00:17.500
Yeah.

00:17.567 --> 00:22.305
Okay. Uh, so, um...
Is this fence new?

00:22.372 --> 00:25.374
Eh... it's a long story.

00:25.442 --> 00:29.779
- Is it a magic story?!
- M-M-M-a-a-a-ybe...?

00:29.846 --> 00:32.682
Well, what happened?!
Tell me. Please?

00:32.749 --> 00:36.519
Okay, okay.
But it's not a happy story.

00:36.586 --> 00:39.188
<i>Amethyst was horsing
around by the cliff.</i>

00:39.256 --> 00:41.791
Amethyst, be careful!

00:41.858 --> 00:44.627
Steven, why you getting so
worked up?

00:44.695 --> 00:47.630
What ... do you care about me or
something?

00:47.698 --> 00:50.232
- Yes!
- Aw, Steven, I

00:50.334 --> 00:52.601
didn't mean to make you ...
whoa-a-a-a-a-a!

00:52.703 --> 00:55.137
Amethyst, stop!
You're gonna fall!

00:55.238 --> 00:57.640
Ooh!
Steven, I'm

00:57.708 --> 00:59.825
- gonna fa-a-ll!
- Amethyst, you're

00:59.910 --> 01:02.378
- gonna get hurt!
- Steven, please.

01:02.412 --> 01:04.580
I'm a gem warrior.
I'm not gonna fa...

01:05.894 --> 01:08.417
Ugh. This is so embarrassing.

01:10.420 --> 01:12.254
<i>I'm okay!</i>

01:12.339 --> 01:15.558
So, I ran down there
as fast as I could.

01:21.898 --> 01:24.600
- Are you sure you're okay?
- Yes, Steven.

01:24.684 --> 01:27.269
I'm fine, except for this!

01:27.354 --> 01:29.105
- Amethyst!
- Great.

01:29.189 --> 01:34.377
- Show me your gem!
- Fresh!

01:34.444 --> 01:36.579
Amethyst, your gem is cracked!

01:36.646 --> 01:39.415
Rude!
It's not a big deal!

01:39.516 --> 01:41.684
Plus, now I have this cool
googly eye!

01:41.752 --> 01:44.286
How did this happen?

01:44.354 --> 01:46.455
She fell off the
cliff by the lighthouse.

01:46.523 --> 01:48.557
- Did not!
- Of course.

01:48.658 --> 01:52.428
How could I have been so blind?
We need to put a fence up there

01:52.496 --> 01:57.600
- so this will never happen again!
- And that's why there's a fence. The end.

01:58.727 --> 02:01.904
- Wait, what happened to Amethyst?
- Uh...

02:01.972 --> 02:05.441
- Come on. Tell me the rest!
- I don't wanna.

02:05.509 --> 02:09.311
Steven?
Steven...

02:09.413 --> 02:11.730
- Mm...
- Steven!

02:14.197 --> 02:17.703
Okay, okay! But only if you
let me try on your glasses.

02:17.821 --> 02:19.872
Only if you give me the rest
of your juice.

02:19.990 --> 02:21.957
Okay, but it's mostly backwash.

02:21.992 --> 02:25.711
- Good enough.
- How do I look?

02:25.829 --> 02:30.766
- I have no idea.
- Well, um, so...

02:30.834 --> 02:32.935
Uh, we were all worried about Amethyst.

02:33.003 --> 02:34.225
So, what's the problem?

02:34.226 --> 02:38.240
- Amethyst falls on stuff all the time.
- It'd be fine if it was

02:38.308 --> 02:40.409
just her body, but her gem is damaged.

02:40.477 --> 02:42.611
So what do you do to fix it?

02:42.679 --> 02:45.347
Before...
we had Rose.

02:45.415 --> 02:48.560
Steven, your mother
had healing tears that

02:48.561 --> 02:51.520
flowed from her gem. She
felt real love for those

02:51.588 --> 02:54.940
around her. She felt real
sorrow when they were hurt.

02:54.941 --> 02:57.335
You have the Rose Quartz gem now.

02:57.336 --> 03:02.226
- I know that power is in you, too.
- Amethyst, show me your gem!

03:02.227 --> 03:03.766
Yeah, all right.

03:03.834 --> 03:07.253
The power to heal.

03:12.242 --> 03:15.461
It's not working. I guess
I'm just too tough to cry.

03:15.545 --> 03:17.963
Just today, you were
crying about snakes.

03:18.048 --> 03:21.423
- They don't have any arms!
- We have no choice.

03:21.424 --> 03:24.797
We need to take Amethyst to
Rose's healing spring.

03:24.860 --> 03:27.389
Guys, I'm fine.
I'm not gonna get any

03:27.474 --> 03:32.394
wor-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r...
r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r-r...

03:32.462 --> 03:35.231
_

03:38.401 --> 03:41.787
And in the center of
the garden ... Rose's fountain,

03:41.872 --> 03:46.408
overflowing with your mother's
healing, lachrymal essence!

03:46.459 --> 03:48.377
- I don't see it.
- Wha...

03:48.445 --> 03:52.122
_

03:52.157 --> 03:53.382
Now, now!

03:53.483 --> 03:56.318
Uh, let's keep it together!
Our memories of Rose can't be

03:56.419 --> 03:58.287
tainted by some overgrown brambles!

03:58.355 --> 04:01.924
Look at them. They're
a mess without her guidance.

04:01.992 --> 04:05.294
Directionless, pathetic,
clinging things.

04:05.362 --> 04:08.497
- It's going to be okay, Garnet.
- Sure.

04:08.565 --> 04:10.299
Y-Y-You really think so?

04:10.367 --> 04:14.820
Healing tears!

04:16.990 --> 04:19.858
Hmm.
Maybe there's a path over here!

04:19.942 --> 04:22.912
_

04:24.000 --> 04:30.074
Advertise your product or brand here
